+
+Possible concerns:
+- The role expects at least 3 years of backend engineering and strong Rust, C/C++, and/or Go.
+- Accessible copies of the posting say applicants must already live in the EU and hold valid EU work authorization.
+
+Fit score: 8/10
+Recommendation: watch
